      "text": "Don't know why I didn't realize this #PowerShell #WebDev #Template trick before....\n\nJust name your variables tags:\n\n~~~PowerShell\n${<head>} = \"<head><title>Hello World</title></head>\"\n${<body>} = \"<body><h1>Hello World</h1></body>\"\n\"<html>${<head>}${<body>}</html>\"\n~~~\n\n🤯😉😎\n\nWorks since v1"
